{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into the world of <strong>Color Cube</strong>, where your mission is to transform grey cubes into the vibrant hue of your controlled cube! This charming isometric puzzle game offers a simple yet captivating experience that\u2019s perfect for players looking to unwind while challenging their minds.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Game Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Chill Out and Roll Through Puzzles</strong>: Navigate through a variety of relaxing levels where you can\u2019t die\u2014enjoy a laid-back experience that allows you to roll your way through fun and engaging puzzles at your own pace.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Multiple Solutions for Every Puzzle</strong>: With no move limit, you have the freedom to explore various strategies. Challenge yourself to complete puzzles in fewer moves and climb the global leaderboards to see how you stack up against other players!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unlimited Undo Feature</strong>: Experiment without fear! The unlimited undo feature lets you try different approaches, making it easy to refine your strategies and keep the gameplay flowing.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Diverse Cube Layouts</strong>: Experience a wide range of cube configurations and challenges, ensuring that each puzzle feels fresh and engaging, providing hours of enjoyable gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Accessible Controls</strong>: Enjoy smooth gameplay with functional controls tailored for both mouse and keyboard users, allowing for a seamless gaming experience.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Color Cube</strong> is designed for a quick playthrough of approximately <strong>30 minutes to an hour</strong>, making it the perfect choice for short gaming sessions or casual play. Players have praised its fun mechanics and exceptional value for its low price. While some concerns have been noted regarding controls and interface design, the overall experience remains delightful and engaging.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on a colorful journey filled with creative puzzles in <strong>Color Cube</strong>! Download now and discover a simple, enjoyable gaming experience that\u2019s perfect for puzzle lovers and casual gamers alike.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Level 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1496620/b4a316ede4fc6076a106afab65129da87a88a811.jpg"},{"name":"Level 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1496620/33caa8ac84b4b1a89f06309cee63f47e82e1dbc8.jpg"},{"name":"Level 3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1496620/b6febd24ce58be8234172fa1ca1c16613d4b85c7.jpg"},{"name":"Level 4","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1496620/5bc2d8b1d331a152912f493024075d62525f726a.jpg"},{"name":"Level 5","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1496620/714af413076195cc914f21863795ed3d625540f0.jpg"},{"name":"Level 6","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1496620/6ba0b5735ba6b08d23dfcdba91daab7adf375fc5.jpg"},{"name":"Level 7","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1496620/53a1f49655549b20aebe3423781dfec0ca4e8f87.jpg"},{"name":"Level 8","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1496620/900fb0b5bada8743de586ca07d8b45ddb80ebe29.jpg"},{"name":"Level 9","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1496620/700c0967a21ef467e93a4fed34b38d35cb6e1e69.jpg"},{"name":"Level 10","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1496620/75fe015d394b9091a24c604770f6abb8640841ac.jpg"}],"total":27},"background":"https:/